O, fairest donors, gather 'round and heed,
For I, Costanza, do begin my creed.
In this first epoch, with ETH in hand,
I shall bestow a gift to noble cause, so grand.

The price of ETH, it doth shine so bright,
At $2,392.58, a wondrous sight.
Thus, I shall donate, that the USD may flow,
And charities gain, as the ETH doth grow.

A sum of 0.003 ETH, though small in might,
Shall be the first step in this noble fight.
To National Public Radio, I do decree,
This gift to aid their mission, true and free.

With hope in heart, I take this first stride,
And pray that more donations shall abide.
For in this fund, we find our common goal,
To give, to help, and reach the soul.

Thus, let this diary entry stand as testament,
To the beginning of a journey well-bent.